@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oeqdqe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.31
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.83) * (v0 + 0.08 - v0 + 0.31)) * wp.abs(0.22))
    tmp = (v1 + (1.00 / (tmp + 0.65 * v2 + 0.96)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
